{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875748487,"sessionID":"ses_2858f6106ffeAtBNfTYMwiEaoo","part":{"id":"prt_d7a716bf1001E1xMVwkT7Kdk2v","messageID":"msg_d7a7160f30012Bve1rnEiTTdXo","sessionID":"ses_2858f6106ffeAtBNfTYMwiEaoo","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_b2088dc2b3394ed59494ccf6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 建立完整的 Makefile 构建目标体系，支持 Go 源码编译、Docker 镜像构建、测试运行、代码检查等开发全生命周期操作，统一入口简化开发者体验。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: ### Background\n12: \n13: AgentCube 项目当前 Makefile 仅包含 Docker 镜像构建目标（AR-032），缺少：\n14: - Go 源码直接编译目标（跨平台二进制）\n15: - 测试执行目标\n16: - 代码检查/格式化目标\n17: - 开发工作流集成目标\n18: \n19: 开发者需要记忆多个独立命令（如 `go build`, `go test`, `golangci-lint`），缺乏统一入口。\n20: \n21: ### Goal\n22: \n23: 扩展 Makefile 为完整的构建工具链：\n24: - 支持 Go 二进制直接编译（支持多平台交叉编译）\n25: - 集成测试、lint、format 等开发工具\n26: - 提供开发/测试/发布等分层工作流\n27: - 与现有 Docker 目标无缝集成\n28: \n29: ### Value\n30: \n31: - **一致性**：所有构建操作通过 `make` 统一入口\n32: - **效率**：常用工作流一键完成（如 `make dev` 启动开发环境）\n33: - **可发现性**：`make help` 显示所有可用目标\n34: - **跨平台**：支持 Linux/Darwin/Windows，交叉编译多架构\n35: - **CI 集成**：便于流水线调用统一构建命令\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## Scope\n40: \n41: ### In-Scope\n42: \n43: | Target Category | Targets | Description |\n44: |-----------------|---------|-------------|\n45: | Binary Build | `build`, `build-router`, `build-workload-manager`, `build-agentd`, `build-picod` | 编译 Go 源码为二进制 |\n46: | Cross-compile | `build-linux-amd64`, `build-linux-arm64`, `build-darwin-amd64`, `build-darwin-arm64` | 跨平台编译 |\n47: | Docker Build | `docker-build`, `docker-build-*` | Docker 镜像构建（现有） |\n48: | Testing | `test`, `test-unit`, `test-integration`, `test-cover` | 运行单元/集成测试 |\n49: | Linting | `lint`, `lint-fix`, `fmt` | 代码检查与格式化 |\n50: | Development | `dev`, `dev-docker`, `watch` | 开发环境启动 |\n51: | Cleanup | `clean`, `docker-clean` | 清理构建产物 |\n52: | Utilities | `help`, `version`, `deps` | 帮助/版本/依赖管理 |\n53: \n54: ### Out-of-Scope\n55: \n56: - CI/CD 流水线配置（独立 AR）\n57: - Helm chart 相关目标（AR-030）\n58: - 发布版本自动化（独立流程）\n59: - 本地 Kubernetes 集群管理\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## Impact Analysis\n64: \n65: ### Dependencies\n66: \n67: | Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n68: |------------|---------|--------|\n69: | Go 1.24+ | 源码编译 | 项目已使用 |\n70: | golangci-lint | 代码检查 | 需引入 |\n71: | gofmt/goimports | 代码格式化 | 标准工具 |\n72: | Docker | 镜像构建 | 已有 |\n73: | kind/kubectl | 本地开发环境 | 外部依赖 |\n74: \n75: ### Upstream\n76: \n77: - `cmd/router/` — Router 源码\n78: - `cmd/workload-manager/` — Workload Manager 源码\n79: - `cmd/agentd/` — Agentd 源码\n80: - `cmd/picod/` — Picod 源码\n81: - `go.mod` / `go.sum` — Go 依赖\n82: \n83: ### Downstream Consumers\n84: \n85: 1. **开发者** — 本地构建、测试、开发\n86: 2. **CI/CD** — 流水线调用统一构建命令\n87: 3. **AR-032** — Docker 构建依赖此 Makefile 扩展\n88: \n89: ### Risks\n90: \n91: | Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n92: |------|----------|------------|\n93: | Makefile 过于复杂 | Medium | 按分类组织，保持简洁，优先常用目标 |\n94: | 跨平台兼容 | Medium | 使用 Go 跨平台特性，避免 shell 依赖 |\n95: | 依赖缺失 | Low | 目标添加依赖检查，友好报错 |\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## Alternatives Considered\n100: \n101: ### Option 1: 保持现状，仅用 Docker 目标（Not Selected）\n102: \n103: **Pros**: 简单，现有目标已满足 Docker 需求\n104: **Cons**: 开发者需单独学习 Go 构建命令，无统一入口\n105: \n106: ### Option 2: 仅添加 Go 编译目标（Not Selected）\n107: \n108: **Pros**: 满足编译需求，简单\n109: **Cons**: 缺少测试、lint 等开发必需功能\n110: \n111: ### Option 3: 完整 Makefile 目标体系（Selected）\n112: \n113: **Pros**: 统一入口，功能完整，符合行业最佳实践\n114: **Cons**: 初始实现工作量较大\n115: \n116: ### Option 4: 使用 goreleaser 或其他工具（Not Selected）\n117: \n118: **Pros**: 功能强大，支持发布\n119: **Cons**: 过度设计，开发阶段不需要；增加外部依赖\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ## Technical Design\n124: \n125: ### 目标层级结构\n126: \n127: ```\n128: Makefile\n129: ├── 基础变量 (DOCKER_REGISTRY, GO_VERSION, BINARY_VERSION 等)\n130: ├── 帮助信息 (通过 self-documenting makefile)\n131: │\n132: ├── build (默认)\n133: │   ├── build-router\n134: │   ├── build-workload-manager\n135: │   ├── build-agentd\n136: │   └── build-picod\n137: │\n138: ├── cross-build (交叉编译)\n139: │   ├── build-linux-amd64\n140: │   ├── build-linux-arm64\n141: │   ├── build-darwin-amd64\n142: │   └── build-darwin-arm64\n143: │\n144: ├── docker-* (Docker 相关)\n145: │   └── 现有目标...\n146: │\n147: ├── test\n148: │   ├── test-unit\n149: │   ├── test-integration\n150: │   └── test-cover\n151: │\n152: ├── lint & fmt\n153: │\n154: ├── dev\n155: │   ├── dev-docker\n156: │   └── dev-kind\n157: │\n158: └── clean & help\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ### 核心目标实现\n162: \n163: #### Binary Build\n164: \n165: ```makefile\n166: # 构建变量\n167: BINARIES := router workload-manager agentd picod\n168: GO_LDFLAGS := -s -w -X main.version=$(BINARY_VERSION)\n169: \n170: # 主构建目标\n171: .PHONY: build\n172: build: $(BINARIES)\n173: \n174: router:\n175: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/router ./cmd/router\n176: \n177: workload-manager:\n178: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/workload-manager ./cmd/workload-manager\n179: \n180: agentd:\n181: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/agentd ./cmd/agentd\n182: \n183: picod:\n184: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/picod ./cmd/picod\n185: ```\n186: \n187: #### Cross-compile\n188: \n189: ```makefile\n190: .PHONY: cross-build\n191: cross-build: build-linux-amd64 build-linux-arm64 build-darwin-amd64 build-darwin-arm64\n192: \n193: build-linux-amd64:\n194: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -o bin/linux-amd64/router ./cmd/router\n195: \t# ... 其他二进制\n196: \n197: build-linux-arm64:\n198: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=arm64 go build -o bin/linux-arm64/router ./cmd/router\n199: \t# ... 其他二进制\n200: # 类似 darwin 目标\n201: ```\n202: \n203: #### Test\n204: \n205: ```makefile\n206: .PHONY: test test-unit test-integration test-cover\n207: test: test-unit\n208: \n209: test-unit:\n210: \tgo test -v -short ./...\n211: \n212: test-integration:\n213: \tgo test -v -tags=integration ./integration/...\n214: \n215: test-cover:\n216: \tgo test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...\n217: \tgo tool cover -html=coverage.out -o coverage.html\n218: ```\n219: \n220: #### Lint & Format\n221: \n222: ```makefile\n223: .PHONY: lint lint-fix fmt\n224: \n225: lint:\n226: \tgolangci-lint run ./...\n227: \n228: lint-fix:\n229: \tgolangci-lint run --fix ./...\n230: \n231: fmt:\n232: \tgofmt -w -s .\n233: \tgoimports -w .\n234: ```\n235: \n236: #### Development\n237: \n238: ```makefile\n239: .PHONY: dev dev-docker\n240: dev: dev-docker\n241: \n242: dev-docker:\n243: \tdocker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d\n244: \n245: dev-kind:\n246: \tkind create cluster --name agentcube\n247: \tkubectl apply -f manifests/\n248: ```\n249: \n250: #### Help (Self-documenting)\n251: \n252: ```makefile\n253: .PHONY: help\n254: help:\n255: \t@echo \"AgentCube Makefile Targets\"\n256: \t@echo \"\"\n257: \t@echo \"Build:\"\n258: \t@echo \"  make build              # Build all binaries for current platform\"\n259: \t@echo \"  make build-<binary>     # Build specific binary (router|workload-manager|agentd|picod)\"\n260: \t@echo \"  make cross-build        # Build for all platforms\"\n261: \t@echo \"\"\n262: \t@echo \"Docker:\"\n263: \t@echo \"  make docker-build       # Build all Docker images\"\n264: \t@echo \"  make docker-push        # Push images to registry\"\n265: \t@echo \"\"\n266: \t@echo \"Test:\"\n267: \t@echo \"  make test               # Run unit tests\"\n268: \t@echo \"  make test-cover         # Run tests with coverage\"\n269: \t@echo \"\"\n270: \t@echo \"Code Quality:\"\n271: \t@echo \"  make lint               # Run linter\"\n272: \t@echo \"  make fmt                # Format code\"\n273: \t@echo \"\"\n274: \t@echo \"Development:\"\n275: \t@echo \"  make dev                # Start development environment\"\n276: \t@echo \"\"\n277: \t@echo \"Utilities:\"\n278: \t@echo \"  make clean              # Clean build artifacts\"\n279: \t@echo \"  make help               # Show this help\"\n280: ```\n281: \n282: ---\n283: \n284: ## Implementation Plan\n285: \n286: ### Phase 1: 扩展基础构建目标\n287: \n288: - [ ] 扩展 `build` 目标支持所有二进制\n289: - [ ] 添加 `build-<binary>` 独立目标\n290: - [ ] 添加跨平台编译目标\n291: \n292: ### Phase 2: 测试与代码质量\n293: \n294: - [ ] 添加 `test`, `test-unit`, `test-cover` 目标\n295: - [ ] 添加 `lint`, `fmt` 目标\n296: - [ ] 配置 golangci-lint config\n297: \n298: ### Phase 3: 开发工作流\n299: \n300: - [ ] 添加 `dev`, `dev-docker` 目标\n301: - [ ] 添加 `watch` 文件监控目标（可选）\n302: \n303: ### Phase 4: 工具与文档\n304: \n305: - [ ] 添加 `help` 自文档目标\n306: - [ ] 添加 `deps` 依赖检查目标\n307: - [ ] 验证所有目标可执行\n308: \n309: ---\n310: \n311: ## Acceptance Criteria\n312: \n313: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n314: |----|----------|-----------------|\n315: | MAKE-001 | 执行 `make build` | 成功编译 router, workload-manager, agentd, picod 到 bin/ 目录 |\n316: | MAKE-002 | 执行 `make build-router` | 仅编译 router 二进制 |\n317: | MAKE-003 | 执行 `make cross-build` | 生成多平台多架构二进制 |\n318: | MAKE-004 | 执行 `make test` | 运行单元测试并报告结果 |\n319: | MAKE-005 | 执行 `make lint` | 运行 golangci-lint 检查代码 |\n320: | MAKE-006 | 执行 `make fmt` | 格式化代码 |\n321: | MAKE-007 | 执行 `make help` | 显示所有可用目标及说明 |\n322: | MAKE-008 | 执行 `make clean` | 清理 bin/、coverage.out 等构建产物 |\n323: | MAKE-009 | Docker 目标仍正常工作 | `make docker-build` 功能不受影响 |\n324: \n325: ---\n326: \n327: ## Relationship to Other ARs\n328: \n329: - **AR-032** — Docker 多阶段构建依赖此 Makefile 的扩展目标\n330: - **AR-030** — Helm chart 部署不受影响\n331: - 独立 AR — CI/CD 流水线将调用 `make` 目标\n332: \n333: ---\n334: \n335: ## Timeline Estimate\n336: \n337: | Phase | Effort |\n338: |-------|--------|\n339: | 基础构建目标 | 1 小时 |\n340: | 测试与代码质量 | 1.5 小时 |\n341: | 开发工作流 | 1 小时 |\n342: | 工具与文档 | 30 分钟 |\n343: | 验证与调试 | 1 小时 |\n344: | **Total** | **5 小时** |\n\n(End of file - total 344 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Summary\n\n建立完整的 Makefile 构建目标体系，支持 Go 源码编译、Docker 镜像构建、测试运行、代码检查等开发全生命周期操作，统一入口简化开发者体验。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nAgentCube 项目当前 Makefile 仅包含 Docker 镜像构建目标（AR-032），缺少：\n- Go 源码直接编译目标（跨平台二进制）\n- 测试执行目标\n- 代码检查/格式化目标\n- 开发工作流集成目标\n\n开发者需要记忆多个独立命令（如 `go build`, `go test`, `golangci-lint`），缺乏统一入口。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775875748468,"end":1775875748484}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775875748514,"sessionID":"ses_2858f6106ffeAtBNfTYMwiEaoo","part":{"id":"prt_d7a717286001Fvy9XOYdIRGkFh","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a7160f30012Bve1rnEiTTdXo","sessionID":"ses_2858f6106ffeAtBNfTYMwiEaoo","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":28453,"input":216,"output":92,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":28145}},"cost":0}}
